<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/3" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style=""></iframe></p>
<p><strong>SCP-CN-1374：蜂与栗</strong></p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3396110&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609720529" alt="Kcorena" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3396110)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;">Kcorena</a></span></p>
<p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/kcorena-s-personnel-file">如果你想了解该作者的更多作品，请点击此处</a></p>
<hr />
<p>图片链接：<a href="https://pixabay.com/zh/photos/chestnut-branch-tree-leaves-5644210/">https://pixabay.com/zh/photos/chestnut-branch-tree-leaves-5644210/</a></p>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
